<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8" standalone="yes"?><rss version="2.0" xmlns:atom="http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom"><channel><title>溶血性贫血 on Aloha's Blog</title><link>https://daisilia.com/series/%E5%86%85%E7%A7%91%E5%AD%A6/%E8%A1%80%E6%B6%B2%E7%96%BE%E7%97%85/%E6%BA%B6%E8%A1%80%E6%80%A7%E8%B4%AB%E8%A1%80/</link><description>Recent content in 溶血性贫血 on Aloha's Blog</description><generator>Hugo -- gohugo.io</generator><language>zh</language><lastBuildDate>Tue, 11 Jul 2023 10:25:42 +0800</lastBuildDate><atom:link href="https://daisilia.com/series/%E5%86%85%E7%A7%91%E5%AD%A6/%E8%A1%80%E6%B6%B2%E7%96%BE%E7%97%85/%E6%BA%B6%E8%A1%80%E6%80%A7%E8%B4%AB%E8%A1%80/index.xml" rel="self" type="application/rss+xml"/><item><title>遗传性球形红细胞增多症</title><link>https://daisilia.com/series/%E5%86%85%E7%A7%91%E5%AD%A6/%E8%A1%80%E6%B6%B2%E7%96%BE%E7%97%85/%E6%BA%B6%E8%A1%80%E6%80%A7%E8%B4%AB%E8%A1%80/%E9%81%97%E4%BC%A0%E6%80%A7%E7%90%83%E5%BD%A2%E7%BA%A2%E7%BB%86%E8%83%9E%E5%A2%9E%E5%A4%9A%E7%97%87/</link><pubDate>Tue, 11 Jul 2023 19:42:45 +0800</pubDate><guid>https://daisilia.com/series/%E5%86%85%E7%A7%91%E5%AD%A6/%E8%A1%80%E6%B6%B2%E7%96%BE%E7%97%85/%E6%BA%B6%E8%A1%80%E6%80%A7%E8%B4%AB%E8%A1%80/%E9%81%97%E4%BC%A0%E6%80%A7%E7%90%83%E5%BD%A2%E7%BA%A2%E7%BB%86%E8%83%9E%E5%A2%9E%E5%A4%9A%E7%97%87/</guid><description>&lt;dl>
&lt;dt>遗传性球形红细胞增多症（hereditary spherocytosis，HS）&lt;/dt>
&lt;dd>一种遗传性红细胞膜缺陷导致的溶血性贫血，临床特点为&lt;em>自幼发生的贫血、间歇性黄疽和脾大&lt;/em>。&lt;/dd>
&lt;/dl>
&lt;p>病理基础为红细胞膜蛋白基因异常，致膜骨架蛋白缺陷，细胞膜脂质丢失，细胞表面积减少，细胞球形变。球形红细胞的变形性和柔韧性降低，当通过脾脏时容易被破坏，出现&lt;em>血管外溶血性贫血&lt;/em>。&lt;/p></description></item><item><title>红细胞葡萄糖-6-磷酸脱氢酶缺乏症</title><link>https://daisilia.com/series/%E5%86%85%E7%A7%91%E5%AD%A6/%E8%A1%80%E6%B6%B2%E7%96%BE%E7%97%85/%E6%BA%B6%E8%A1%80%E6%80%A7%E8%B4%AB%E8%A1%80/%E7%BA%A2%E7%BB%86%E8%83%9E%E8%91%A1%E8%90%84%E7%B3%96-6-%E7%A3%B7%E9%85%B8%E8%84%B1%E6%B0%A2%E9%85%B6%E7%BC%BA%E4%B9%8F%E7%97%87/</link><pubDate>Tue, 11 Jul 2023 19:51:32 +0800</pubDate><guid>https://daisilia.com/series/%E5%86%85%E7%A7%91%E5%AD%A6/%E8%A1%80%E6%B6%B2%E7%96%BE%E7%97%85/%E6%BA%B6%E8%A1%80%E6%80%A7%E8%B4%AB%E8%A1%80/%E7%BA%A2%E7%BB%86%E8%83%9E%E8%91%A1%E8%90%84%E7%B3%96-6-%E7%A3%B7%E9%85%B8%E8%84%B1%E6%B0%A2%E9%85%B6%E7%BC%BA%E4%B9%8F%E7%97%87/</guid><description>&lt;p>已发现的 20 余种遗传性红细胞酶病中最常见的一种。&lt;/p></description></item><item><title>自身免疫性溶血性贫血</title><link>https://daisilia.com/series/%E5%86%85%E7%A7%91%E5%AD%A6/%E8%A1%80%E6%B6%B2%E7%96%BE%E7%97%85/%E6%BA%B6%E8%A1%80%E6%80%A7%E8%B4%AB%E8%A1%80/%E8%87%AA%E8%BA%AB%E5%85%8D%E7%96%AB%E6%80%A7%E6%BA%B6%E8%A1%80%E6%80%A7%E8%B4%AB%E8%A1%80/</link><pubDate>Wed, 12 Jul 2023 22:09:53 +0800</pubDate><guid>https://daisilia.com/series/%E5%86%85%E7%A7%91%E5%AD%A6/%E8%A1%80%E6%B6%B2%E7%96%BE%E7%97%85/%E6%BA%B6%E8%A1%80%E6%80%A7%E8%B4%AB%E8%A1%80/%E8%87%AA%E8%BA%AB%E5%85%8D%E7%96%AB%E6%80%A7%E6%BA%B6%E8%A1%80%E6%80%A7%E8%B4%AB%E8%A1%80/</guid><description>&lt;p>根据无病因分为原发性和继发性 AIHA；根据致病抗体最佳活性温度分为&lt;a href="#%e6%b8%a9%e6%8a%97%e4%bd%93%e5%9e%8b-aiha">温抗体型&lt;/a>（80%&amp;ndash;90%）和&lt;a href="#%e5%86%b7%e6%8a%97%e4%bd%93%e5%9e%8b-aiha">冷抗体型&lt;/a>。&lt;/p></description></item><item><title>阵发性睡眠性血红蛋白尿症</title><link>https://daisilia.com/series/%E5%86%85%E7%A7%91%E5%AD%A6/%E8%A1%80%E6%B6%B2%E7%96%BE%E7%97%85/%E6%BA%B6%E8%A1%80%E6%80%A7%E8%B4%AB%E8%A1%80/%E9%98%B5%E5%8F%91%E6%80%A7%E7%9D%A1%E7%9C%A0%E6%80%A7%E8%A1%80%E7%BA%A2%E8%9B%8B%E7%99%BD%E5%B0%BF%E7%97%87/</link><pubDate>Wed, 12 Jul 2023 22:08:24 +0800</pubDate><guid>https://daisilia.com/series/%E5%86%85%E7%A7%91%E5%AD%A6/%E8%A1%80%E6%B6%B2%E7%96%BE%E7%97%85/%E6%BA%B6%E8%A1%80%E6%80%A7%E8%B4%AB%E8%A1%80/%E9%98%B5%E5%8F%91%E6%80%A7%E7%9D%A1%E7%9C%A0%E6%80%A7%E8%A1%80%E7%BA%A2%E8%9B%8B%E7%99%BD%E5%B0%BF%E7%97%87/</guid><description>&lt;dl>
&lt;dt>阵发性睡眠性血红蛋白尿症（paroxysmal nocturnal hemoglobinuria，PNH）&lt;/dt>
&lt;dd>是一种&lt;em>后天获得性&lt;/em>的造血干细胞基因突变所致的&lt;em>红细胞膜缺陷&lt;/em>（缺乏 CD55 和 CD59）性溶血病，是一种&lt;em>良性克隆性疾病&lt;/em>。&lt;/dd>
&lt;/dl>
&lt;p>临床表现以&lt;em>血管内溶血性&lt;/em>贫血为主，可伴有血栓形成（机制不明）和骨髓衰竭。典型病人有特征性&lt;strong>间歇发作的睡眠后血红蛋白尿&lt;/strong>（睡眠时体内酸性物质增加）。&lt;/p>
&lt;p>红细胞膜缺乏 CD55 和 CD59，是 PNH 发生血管内溶血的基础。&lt;/p></description></item></channel></rss>